        <p>Advanced AcousticWerkes (AAW) is a Singapore-based IEM manufacturer founded in 2014 by Kevin Wang. AAW designs and builds custom and universal in-ear monitors across dynamic, balanced armature, electrostatic, planar, and hybrid platforms.</p>
        <p>Mockingbird is the successor to the acclaimed W900 and represents AAW's nine-driver hybrid reference flagship: proprietary tuned dynamic woofer, bespoke super tweeter armatures, TrueXross 4-way crossover, and precision-engineered acoustic chambers. High-end speaker-like performance — universal or custom.</p>
